Class RiskPlayerModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • risk.model.RiskPlayerModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class RiskPlayerModel
extends java.util.Observable
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents the model class of the Player. Player has army name, index, territories he occupies, and cards that he owns.
